Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.90,0:00:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Your attention, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.23,0:00:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,This plane will be landing\Nwithin 20 minutes...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.97,0:00:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,...at the New Tokyo\NInternational Airport.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.29,0:00:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's that woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.79,0:00:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomoko Nagata,\Nshe's 28 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.56,0:00:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,A successful\Ndetective in the U. S.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.27,0:00:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,She's so good\Nthat she solved a case...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.44,0:00:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,...which even\Nthe FBI couldn't solve.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.35,0:00:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,So why do we\Nhave to meet her?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.95,0:00:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The mayor himself\Ninvited her.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.49,0:00:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,This means you may\Nfinally lose your job...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.06,0:00:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,...investigating St. Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.47,0:00:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,She must be a very\Nold-fashioned, homely...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.34,0:00:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,...and unpleasant woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.18,0:00:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry that I'm\Nan unpleasant woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.64,0:01:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,PHANTASMAL MASTERPIECE!\NA WOMAN DETECTIVE IS BACK
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.02,0:01:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.26,0:01:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,...about the mysterious\Nthief St. Tail?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.73,0:01:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,She uses magic freely...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.07,0:01:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,...and she sends\Na warning note prior to her crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.77,0:01:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,No one knows her identity.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.91,0:01:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.05,0:01:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Impressive!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.12,0:01:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we can talk now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.85,0:01:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to ask you\Nfor your assistance...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.89,0:01:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,...in catching St. Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.93,0:01:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I've assured you\Nthat I'll catch her!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.04,0:01:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I expect you\Ncan catch her someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.58,0:01:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,But in this case...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.75,0:01:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,...I think it's better\Nto ask this lovely lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.13,0:01:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.67,0:01:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,...but I came back to Japan\Non a personal matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.91,0:01:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you make any\Narrangements to help us?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.68,0:01:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.75,0:01:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,To-mo-ko!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.19,0:02:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I can give you a ride.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.20,0:02:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.93,0:02:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,...that I can't assist you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.74,0:02:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.37,0:02:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I definitely will\Narrest St. Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.55,0:02:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the person\Nwho will catch her!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.59,0:02:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Be quiet! This kind\Nof thing is done by age.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.19,0:02:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That's unfair! All of a sudden\Nyou're motivated!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.20,0:02:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomoko has sparked\Nthe detective fire in me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.57,0:02:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nice to see a father\Nand son together.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.54,0:02:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, Asuka Jr. ...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.11,0:02:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,...you go to St. Paulia's, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.02,0:02:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What? How did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.56,0:02:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Your uniform.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.23,0:02:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, could you show me\Naround the school?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.10,0:02:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.77,0:02:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The graph for y=2x\Nis a straight line...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.51,0:02:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,...which runs through the origin.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.72,0:02:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what\Nhappened to Asuka Jr.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.29,0:02:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,He's healthy and has\Nnever missed any classes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.53,0:02:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,He was summoned\Nby the mayor...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.70,0:02:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,...according to Takamiya.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.44,0:02:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That means it must have\Nsomething to do with St. Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.98,0:03:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Asuka Jr. is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.62,0:03:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,...walking with a really\Nbeautiful woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.19,0:03:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.63,0:03:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,She's really beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.07,0:03:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know that he\Nlikes older women.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.01,0:03:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?\NGo back to your seats!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.28,0:03:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Nagata...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.05,0:03:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know her, Sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.05,0:03:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. She was\Nthe smartest student...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.56,0:03:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,...in the history of this school.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.06,0:03:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,If I remember correctly...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.23,0:03:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,...she went to a college in the U.S.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.24,0:03:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know\Nabout her, Seira?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.75,0:03:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard rumors about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.15,0:03:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,She was the famous daughter...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.79,0:03:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,...of a rich family in this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.66,0:03:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,On the hill from where\Nyou can see the port...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.76,0:03:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,...there is a big\NEuropean-style house.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.83,0:03:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean that\Nhaunted house?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.74,0:03:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. She used to live there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.24,0:03:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,But the people who\Nlived there are missing...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.68,0:03:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,...aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.08,0:03:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the rumor, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.95,0:03:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard she's\Na famous detective now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.76,0:04:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! A detective?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.78,0:04:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Just beyond here, I've found\Na really cute trinket store.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.52,0:04:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Meimi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.56,0:04:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah,\Nbut I have homework...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.70,0:04:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a little peek.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.10,0:04:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's Tomoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.61,0:04:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder where she's going.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.21,0:04:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's follow her!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.68,0:04:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! But...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.32,0:04:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,- Don't worry!\N- Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.36,0:04:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did she go?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.60,0:04:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't this\Nthe haunted house?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.21,0:04:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard that a first-year\Nstudent in our school...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.91,0:04:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,...heard a woman crying\Nin the middle of night.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.25,0:04:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.80,0:04:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We met earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.67,0:04:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.54,0:04:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomoko Nagata.\NNice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.95,0:05:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I'm Meimi Haneoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.42,0:05:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,A delicate\Nand beautiful hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.56,0:05:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,People who have\Nhands like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.06,0:05:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,...are often magicians.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.67,0:05:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you like to come in?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.80,0:05:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.68,0:05:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.03,0:05:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,A lot of my memories\Nare from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.23,0:05:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,In your eyes, this must\Nbe like a haunted house.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.41,0:05:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.84,0:05:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,They were\Nunderstanding parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.18,0:05:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,When I said\NI wanted to study abroad...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.42,0:05:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,...they let me do it\Nwithout saying anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.52,0:05:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.13,0:05:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go upstairs!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.48,0:05:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.42,0:05:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I was always dreaming.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.99,0:05:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,From here...\Nfrom this window...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.73,0:05:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,...I wanted to fly away.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.17,0:06:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to go somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.37,0:06:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't notice...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.41,0:06:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,...my parents' love for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.84,0:06:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Your parents are...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.68,0:06:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Missing.\NSince I went abroad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.09,0:06:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.16,0:06:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no reason\Nto tell you these things.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.23,0:06:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Please forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.72,0:06:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.22,0:06:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry\NI came in without asking.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.20,0:06:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It brought back\Na lot of memories, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.20,0:06:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Please stay\Nas long as you'd like.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.17,0:06:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,To tell you the truth,\NI don't deserve to be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.01,0:06:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, would you\Nlike to tell me why?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.42,0:06:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Revenge?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.76,0:06:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.23,0:06:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The person\Nwho is responsible...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.73,0:06:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,...for my parents'\Ndisappearance.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.07,0:06:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I only came back here\Nto get my revenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.01,0:06:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,My parents were\Nart dealers in this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.88,0:06:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Art dealers?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.15,0:07:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Those people\Nwho sell pieces of art?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.29,0:07:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.27,0:07:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,My father was\Nstrict but affectionate.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.74,0:07:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother was always\Nwatching over me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.02,0:07:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I was really happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.32,0:07:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The piece of art my parents\Ntreasured most was...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.43,0:07:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,...a picture titled\N"Wings of Freedom."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.33,0:07:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,But a man who wanted...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.44,0:07:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,..."Wings of Freedom"\Nappeared one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.21,0:07:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, my parents\Nturned down his offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.75,0:07:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,But in the end,\Nthey gave in to his enthusiasm...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.75,0:07:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,...and they decided\Nto sell it to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.66,0:07:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,My father though that\Nhe would treasure the picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.26,0:07:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,But the man betrayed\Nmy father's trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.01,0:07:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,He said the picture\Nhe bought was a fake...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.21,0:07:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,...and he sued my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.51,0:07:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.88,0:07:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Because my father\Ndidn't have...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.09,0:07:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,...any evidence\Nto prove otherwise...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.83,0:07:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,...he had to pay a lot\Nof money and apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.90,0:07:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of that he lost\Ncredibility as an art dealer...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.27,0:08:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,...and he lost everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.21,0:08:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why they disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.31,0:08:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,As I was abroad...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.85,0:08:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,...I didn't know what was going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.99,0:08:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,But I have always believed...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.33,0:08:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,...that my parents were innocent.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.70,0:08:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,But in order to prove it...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.27,0:08:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,...I didn't know what I could do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.11,0:08:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why you\Nbecame a detective?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.68,0:08:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,In order to become\Nstrong and take revenge...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.15,0:08:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,...I endured the difficult training.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.10,0:08:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I continued to investigate...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.30,0:08:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,...the man who deceived...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.81,0:08:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,...my parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.34,0:08:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,And the man is...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.12,0:08:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,He's the owner\Nof Sugawara Industries...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.22,0:08:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,...Ryosuke Sugawara.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.09,0:08:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,She's going to steal?!\NNo way!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.46,0:08:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,If she can prove\Nthat Sugawara...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.53,0:08:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,...has the real\N"Wings of Freedom"...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.77,0:08:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,...then she can prove\Nher parents' innocence.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.31,0:08:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,No! She shouldn't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.32,0:08:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Meimi...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.62,0:09:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll steal the picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.66,0:09:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll steal it\Nbefore Tomoko can...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.53,0:09:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,...and reveal\NSugawara's crime!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.70,0:09:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Her revenge is meaningless.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.38,0:09:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.70,0:09:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Today I'd like to take you around,\Naway from the job.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.47,0:09:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.38,0:09:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think you've seen enough\Nwith this boy as a guide.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.71,0:09:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,This time I'd like to show you\Nan adult's hospitality...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.85,0:09:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,"I'm taking\N'Wings of Freedom'...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.58,0:09:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,...that's in the possession\Nof Mr. Ryosuke Sugawara.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.65,0:09:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,-St. Tail"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.99,0:09:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,- She is...!\N- What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.78,0:10:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The real "Wings of Freedom"\Nis in my possession?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.85,0:10:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that what you're saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.99,0:10:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.59,0:10:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,That's silly!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.10,0:10:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I've always wanted that piece...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.80,0:10:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of that,\NI once bought a counterfeit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.88,0:10:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're saying\Nyou don't have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.28,0:10:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course I don't have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.02,0:10:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the one who wants\Nto know where it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.10,0:10:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard of\Nthe mysterious thief St. Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.47,0:10:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,She must have\Nmisunderstood something.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.01,0:10:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,She is...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.42,0:10:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like St. Tail to send\Nan inaccurate warning note.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.69,0:10:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You believe\Nthat petty thief's words?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.30,0:10:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,She isn't a petty thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.71,0:10:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What Asuka Jr. said is true.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.24,0:10:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,According to my research...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.71,0:10:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,...St. Tail has never sent\Nan inaccurate warning note.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.09,0:10:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Not even once!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.76,0:11:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,If you let us search your house,\Nwe can clear this up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.47,0:11:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I must refuse!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.14,0:11:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.51,0:11:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,If you haven't done\Nanything wrong...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.27,0:11:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,...it shouldn't be a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.21,0:11:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it isn't necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.85,0:11:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't even\Nhave any evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.59,0:11:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Chairman. It's almost time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.89,0:11:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.30,0:11:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Detective Asuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.43,0:11:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll listen to your advice...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.10,0:11:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,...and will let you\Nguard the outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.01,0:11:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we'll do so.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.75,0:11:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't she that\Nart dealer's daughter?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.32,0:11:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I had it confirmed...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.05,0:11:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,...through an American\Ndetective agency...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.89,0:11:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,...and there's no doubt about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.56,0:11:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently she's been\Ninvestigating you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.47,0:11:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.57,0:11:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,If she finds out\NI have the real picture...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.21,0:11:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Then...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.58,0:11:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't even need to ask!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.85,0:11:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.86,0:11:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Lord, forgive me,\Nfor I use no gimmick or trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.67,0:11:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,One!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.25,0:12:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.52,0:12:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.15,0:12:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful, Meimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.12,0:12:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't know\Nwhat Tomoko will do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.06,0:12:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry! It'll be fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.60,0:12:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,May the blessings\Nof God be with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.49,0:12:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Asuka Jr., where is\NDetective Asuka?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.89,0:12:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,He told me\Nhe had something...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.66,0:12:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,...he needed to check...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.50,0:12:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What is he going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.00,0:13:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose she gave up...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.04,0:13:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretty impressive, St. Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.63,0:13:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't let you interfere\Nwith my revenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.94,0:13:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.04,0:13:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,She's up in this tree!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.38,0:13:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no! How?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.59,0:13:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Asuka Jr.!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.93,0:13:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Darn it! Never mind!\NLet's move in!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.20,0:13:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.34,0:13:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What shall I do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.16,0:13:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.04,0:13:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You saved me!\NThank you, Asuka Jr.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.53,0:14:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the "Wings of Freedom"\Nyou were looking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.54,0:14:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The real one.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.34,0:14:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the one\Nyour father sold to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.92,0:14:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I prepared the counterfeit\Nand switched them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.59,0:14:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that you've seen the picture\Nyou were looking for...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.73,0:14:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,...you don't have\Nany regrets, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.43,0:14:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The one who broke in\Nshould have been St. Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.10,0:14:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,So, even if you disappear...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.61,0:14:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,...no one will suspect me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.51,0:14:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,After the police leave...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.78,0:14:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,...I'll decide how\Nyou should disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.00,0:15:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,We've made the police leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.57,0:15:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,But the media is making a fuss.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.01,0:15:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess it would be better\Nto give them an explanation.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.58,0:15:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's have a press conference.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.62,0:15:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,This must be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.13,0:15:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,St. Tail...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.41,0:15:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.61,0:15:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You know that I set you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.40,0:15:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.47,0:15:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go! Let go of my hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.51,0:15:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.95,0:15:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.06,0:15:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You almost did it, didn't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.77,0:15:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.62,0:15:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,St. Tail...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.15,0:16:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, but I can't\Ngive this picture to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.56,0:16:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.76,0:16:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't steal!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.60,0:16:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.67,0:16:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Asuka Jr.!\NWhere are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.98,0:16:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Over here! Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.69,0:16:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.20,0:16:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,...Show...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.24,0:16:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,...Time!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.11,0:17:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.00,0:17:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,A thief by the name of St. Tail...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.37,0:17:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,...seems to have\Nbeen misinformed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.77,0:17:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Both six years ago and today...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.84,0:17:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,...I've been a victim.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.78,0:17:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't really have\N"Wings of Freedom," do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.05,0:17:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.39,0:17:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,If you have any doubt...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.82,0:17:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,...please go ahead and search\Nmy house or my company.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.31,0:17:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a nice touch, Tajima...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.59,0:17:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I, Ryosuke Sugawara,\Nswear to God...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.19,0:17:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,...that I am innocent!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.94,0:17:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the real\N"Wings of Freedom"!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.55,0:17:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,- What?!\N- Please explain this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.53,0:18:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know!\NI don't know anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.03,0:18:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Sugawara.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.20,0:18:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Please come with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.14,0:18:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you discussed this\Nwith the mayor?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.91,0:18:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe you should\Nhave a discussion...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.55,0:18:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,...with your conscience.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.82,0:18:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,We've uncovered\Na few things about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.83,0:18:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The materials she\Ngave us helped a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.80,0:18:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll have a lot of time\Nto tell us your story.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.25,0:18:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, St. Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.59,0:18:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard that\NSugawara admitted...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.29,0:18:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,...deceiving your parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.93,0:18:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,My dad was quite pleased.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.03,0:18:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.67,0:18:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Please thank your father for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.08,0:18:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.51,0:18:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Meimi...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.58,0:19:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.02,0:19:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm cheering\Nfor you from America.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.43,0:19:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the connection\Nbetween you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.50,0:19:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,We're best friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.27,0:19:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know... Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.08,0:19:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't understand.\NGuys don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.58,0:19:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! Hey, Meimi!
